import React from 'react';
import TestimonialsPage from './TestimonialsPage'
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
import { Grid, Segment, Image, Header} from 'semantic-ui-react'

const Home = () =>{
    
     
    return(
        <Grid verticalAlign='top' columns={1} stackable >
        <Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Column>
            <Segment raised size="large">
                <Header as="h3" style={textOnly}>Be-Youtiful at a reasonable Price</Header>
                <Image src="../assets/puse.jpeg" alt="lips"/>
            </Segment>
            </Grid.Column>
            
            <Grid.Column>
            <TestimonialsPage />
            </Grid.Column>
            

        </Grid.Row>
        </Grid>
    )
}


const textOnly = {
    fontFamily: 'minion-pro-italic, sans-serif',
    fontStyle: 'normal',
    fontWeight: 500,
    color: ""
  }

export default Home
